&lt;h2&gt;Technician (Endoscopy Decontamination Unit)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone to work as a collection and delivery service person for the Sterile Services department, which is part of the Hospital Sterilization &amp; Disinfection Unit. The role is full time days, Monday-Friday.The ideal candidate will be someone who is in very good physical condition to carry out daily collection and delivery of surgical instruments to the Theatres, Outpatients and other customers of the HSDU service.&lt;/p&gt;
